## Why This Is Asked
Tests ability to design a secure, multi-account GitOps pipeline with image signing, SBOM attestations, and policy enforcement, plus real-world rollback.

## Key Concepts
- GitOps with FluxCD, Helm
- Container image signing (cosign) and SBOM attestations
- Open Policy Agent (Gatekeeper) for policy checks
- Canary deployments and automatic rollback
- Multi-account IAM and artifact attestation storage

## Code Example
```javascript
// FluxCD HelmRelease (simplified)
{
  apiVersion: "helm.toolkit.fluxcd.io/v2beta1",
